{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──第11周的早晨。\n龙姐的身体已经到了没有治疗就无法正常生活的程度。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（第11周…快3个月了。龙姐完全离不开我了。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（多亏了这个，经营也稳定下来了…全都是托龙姐的福。）"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "…来了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "龙姐！…话说，您看起来心情不太好。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "…是啊。都怪你。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "诶？怪我？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…前几天的事。教训手下的时候…突然想起了你的治疗。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "教训手下的时候…？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "是啊。然后…手就…没力气了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "手下居然说'姐，您今天好温柔啊'…我要杀了他。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（教训人都变温柔了…她到底有多想着治疗的事啊…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "高利贷老板工作的时候满脑子都是这种事…该死…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "说明我的治疗确实有效啊。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…别得意。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…但还有更糟糕的事…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "更糟糕？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…你的声音…打电话预约的时候…一听到你的声音…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "听到我的声音后？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…当场…内裤就湿了…只是听到声音…身体就自己…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（气味之后是声音…五感一个接一个被我支配了…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…上周是气味。这次是声音。…我的身体到底怎么了…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "嗅觉、听觉…下一个会是什么呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "别说得那么开心…！",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…所以说…我想了。这样下去不行。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "想到什么对策了？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "…我想如果自己学会的话，就不用来这里了…所以开始学整体按摩了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "学按摩！？龙姐您？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "是啊。买了书，也买了教学DVD。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "教学DVD？请问…叫什么系列？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯…叫'变态按摩师的手法'系列。出了20多卷，评价看起来不错，就全买了。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（'变态按摩师的手法'…！？那…完全是成人片啊…！！）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…龙姐。那个…您看了吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "全看了。一开始还认真地边看边做笔记来着…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "边做笔记…"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…看到一半…感觉…不太对劲了…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "不对劲是…"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…………那是成人片…对吧…？",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…看标题不就知道了吗…'变态按摩师'啊…"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "吵、吵死了！我对那方面不了解啊…！封面上女的做出那种表情我还以为是按摩太舒服了才那样的…！",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（高利贷老板觉得成人片封面是'因为按摩太舒服了'…太单纯了…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "…那，发现之后呢？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "………………。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "您说全看完了吧？发现之后也…？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…………停不下来了……看着看着就联想到你的治疗了……",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（高利贷老板把按摩成人片全部看完…还做了笔记…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…看的时候一直…身体好烫…感觉你在碰我…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "…而且还不止这些…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "还有啊…？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "…手下拿文件到我房间的时候…那堆DVD和笔记本…就在桌上…",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "被看到了…？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "'姐…这么多DVD是啥啊……等等……变态按摩师的……？'他说…",
      "outfit": "suit"
